        <item>
            <title>土力工程处制中学地理数码教材　高清呈现香港常见岩石立体影像</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/06/cedd-made-hd-rock-teaching-materials/life-tech/school/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=cedd-made-hd-rock-teaching-materials</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/06/cedd-made-hd-rock-teaching-materials/life-tech/school/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 10:15:08 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[校园科技]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1203202</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>土力工程处与教育局合作推出全新中学地理数码教材，引入数码化元素如使用摄影测量技术，重现香港常见的岩石之高清立体影像，供教师作教学用途，便利学生学习、认识及观察香港岩石。</p><p><img decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203230" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕撷取画面-2023-11-06-172524-694x575.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="575" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕撷取画面-2023-11-06-172524-694x575.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕撷取画面-2023-11-06-172524-1086x900.jpg 1086w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕撷取画面-2023-11-06-172524-768x636.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕撷取画面-2023-11-06-172524.jpg 1277w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203224" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕撷取画面-2023-11-06-172122-601x580.jpg" alt="" width="601" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕撷取画面-2023-11-06-172122-601x580.jpg 601w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕撷取画面-2023-11-06-172122-932x900.jpg 932w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕撷取画面-2023-11-06-172122-768x742.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕撷取画面-2023-11-06-172122.jpg 1253w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 601px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203225" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕撷取画面-2023-11-06-172216-648x580.jpg" alt="" width="648" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕撷取画面-2023-11-06-172216-648x580.jpg 648w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕撷取画面-2023-11-06-172216-1006x900.jpg 1006w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕撷取画面-2023-11-06-172216-768x687.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕撷取画面-2023-11-06-172216.jpg 1276w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 648px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲土力工程处利用测量技术制作之岩石高清立体影像，图片来源：<a href="https://cedd.modernedu.hk/category/multimedia-learning-materials-chi/3d_rocks/">CEDD</a></p><p>早前土力工程处邀请地理科教师担任顾问，建议如何改善地理科教材。土力工程处其后按照教师建议，拍摄并制作粮船湾、蒲台岛及东平洲三个偏远地区的的全景模式虚拟地质考察路线，让教师安排虚拟考察供学生随时参加，同时亦有助教师安排实地考察前做足准备。3 条全景虚拟地质考察路线覆盖本港 3 大常见岩石：火山岩、花岗岩及沉积岩。另外土力工程处亦根据教育局课程大纲编排，在新教材中加入防治山泥倾泻及斜坡管理等知识。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203227" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕撷取画面-2023-11-06-172352-694x360.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="360" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕撷取画面-2023-11-06-172352-694x360.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕撷取画面-2023-11-06-172352-768x398.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕撷取画面-2023-11-06-172352.jpg 1277w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203229" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕撷取画面-2023-11-06-172442-596x580.jpg" alt="" width="596" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕撷取画面-2023-11-06-172442-596x580.jpg 596w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕撷取画面-2023-11-06-172442-925x900.jpg 925w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕撷取画面-2023-11-06-172442-768x748.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕撷取画面-2023-11-06-172442.jpg 1274w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 596px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲土力工程处利用测量技术制作之全景虚拟地质考察路线，图片来源：<a href="https://cedd.modernedu.hk/category/multimedia-learning-materials-chi/3d_rocks/">CEDD</a></p><p>商业电台引述土力工程处副处长（港岛）张秉业指，新教材让学生可以轻松接触到不同石头样本，从而更容易接触及研究相关内容，如组成岩石的物质等。土力工程处发言人表示，极端天气下，有必要提高社区对抵抗山泥倾泻等灾害之能力，盼望全新数码教材有助学生充分掌握有关斜坡安全的知识，并加深他们在地理方面的认知，从而提升学生防灾意识及警觉性。</p><p>图片、资料来源：<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1726652-20231106.htm">RTHK</a>、<a href="https://www.881903.com/news/local/2509032/%E5%9C%9F%E5%8A%9B%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E8%99%95%E5%8A%A9%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%E5%9C%B0%E7%90%86%E6%95%99%E6%9D%90-%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0">商业电台</a>、<a href="https://cedd.modernedu.hk/category/multimedia-learning-materials-chi/">土木工程拓展署</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/11/06/cedd-made-hd-rock-teaching-materials/life-tech/school/">土力工程处制中学地理数码教材　高清呈现香港常见岩石立体影像</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
