        <item>
            <title>PS5 Slim 外国拆机，散热设计更完善</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/06/ps5-slim-3/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ps5-slim-3</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/06/ps5-slim-3/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Christy]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 10:10:20 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[PS5]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[PS5 Slim]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SONY]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1203180</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Sony 全新 PS5 Slim 即将于 11 月 10 日在美国率先推出。不过离推出前 5 日，YouTube 上已出现 PS5 Slim 评测，称 PS5 Slim 的新设计比 PS5 小很多。</p><p>外国频道「Dave2D」早前在 YouTube 上载名为「全新 Sony PS5 「Slim」-拆解+感想」的影片。展示 PS5 Slim 的修长机身，而全新的主机外壳则采用半哑光半亮面设计，共分为 4 部分，因此用家不能将 PS5 的主机盖套用至 PS5 Slim 上。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-06-07.28.40.png"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203192" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-06-07.28.40-694x374.png" alt="" width="694" height="374" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-06-07.28.40-694x374.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-06-07.28.40-1280x690.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-06-07.28.40-768x414.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-06-07.28.40-1536x828.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-06-07.28.40.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Dave2D 在片中特别提到 PS5 及 PS5 Slim 的重量差异，数码版及光碟版 PS5 分别重 3.3 公斤及 3.9 公斤，而 PS5 Slim 则分别重 2.6 公斤及 3.2 公斤。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-06-07.22.02.png"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203190" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-06-07.22.02-694x350.png" alt="" width="694" height="350" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-06-07.22.02-694x350.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-06-07.22.02-1280x645.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-06-07.22.02-768x387.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-06-07.22.02-1536x774.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-06-07.22.02.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Dave2D 指出，PS5 Slim 以 PS5 的主机内部机构作基础，再加以小调整，以延续 PS5 主机内部机构的设计概念。PS5 及 PS5 Slim 皆利用主机上半部中间的鼓风扇散热。不过 PS5 Slim 的 M.2 NVMe SSD 转移至风扇后方，而光碟机位则安置在主机右下方的护盖下，用家只需开启护盖便能可拆卸光碟机位。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-06-09.15.07.png"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203222" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-06-09.15.07-694x364.png" alt="" width="694" height="364" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-06-09.15.07-694x364.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-06-09.15.07-1280x671.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-06-09.15.07-768x403.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-06-09.15.07-1536x805.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-06-09.15.07.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>至于 PS5 Slim 的内部散热功能，亦如 PS5 般采用两面配置的散热器。配备 5 条导热管及 2 块散热片的液态金属热介面散热器则用作处理晶片，而负责 VRM 供电回路的散热分别装有 1 条导热管及 1 块散热片。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-06-09.17.38.png"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203223" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-06-09.17.38-694x364.png" alt="" width="694" height="364" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-06-09.17.38-694x364.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-06-09.17.38-1280x671.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-06-09.17.38-768x403.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-06-09.17.38-1536x805.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-06-09.17.38.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>为了提升散热效率，所有 PS5 Slim 的散热片皆围著风扇四周，M.2 NVMe SSD 亦更贴近鼓风扇，以增加机身内的冷却气流。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-06-09.26.50.png"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203232" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-06-09.26.50-694x364.png" alt="" width="694" height="364" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-06-09.26.50-694x364.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-06-09.26.50-1280x671.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-06-09.26.50-768x403.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-06-09.26.50-1536x805.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕截图-2023-11-06-09.26.50.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>虽然 Sony 为 PS5 及 PS5 Slim 用家提供横向使用的底座，但纵向使用 PS5 Slim 的用家则需另外加购底座。 Dave2D 又指由于新机功耗略高，因此推算 PS5 Slim<b></b>没有采用新晶片。</p><p>Sony 早前曾表示，预计今年圣诞节将是有史以来游戏机销售最好的季节之一。因此 PS5 在自 2020 年 11 月推出以来，首次出现供多于求的情况。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_38058"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/tCGZ6pkbD5E?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;controls=1&#038;color=white&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;rel=0&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>图片来源：影片截图</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/the-ps5-slim-is-not-that-much-smaller-than-its-chunkier-sibling-according-to-this-new-teardown-video">Eurogamer</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/11/06/ps5-slim-3/fun-tech/">PS5 Slim 外国拆机，散热设计更完善</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
